{"word":"Fig","slug":"fig","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Fig</b> Common to Palestine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=23'>Num 13:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=8&verse=8'>Deu 8:8</a><br/> Common to Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=33'>Psa 105:33</a><br/> Employed as a remedy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=20&verse=7'>2Ki 20:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=38&verse=21'>Isa 38:21</a><br/> Traffic in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=15'>Neh 13:15</a><br/> Dried and preserved<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=30&verse=12'>1Sa 30:12</a><br/> Cakes of, sent by Abigail to David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=25&verse=35'>1Sa 25:35</a><br/> Aprons made of fig leaves, by Adam and Eve<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=7'>Gen 3:7</a>"}]}